      public Article(String author, String journal, String title, String year, String volume, String number, String pages, String keywords, String doi, String ISSN, String month, int index)
      Constructor takes in parameters and creates a new Article object
      Parameters:
      author - name of author of the article.
      journal - type of journal(IEEE, ACM, NJ)
      title - name of the article
      year - year article was published
      volume - volume of article.
      number - number of article.
      pages - pages of article.
      keywords - keywords of article.
      doi - doi of article.
      ISSN - ISSN of article.
      month - month article was published.
      index - index of article in Latex
